      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be an individual farmer, cooperative society, self-help group, or joint liability group. \n1. The cooperative society, self-help group, or joint liability group having a minimum of 10 members. \n1. The applicant must possess a Family Identity Card (Parivar Pehchan Patra).\n1. The applicant must obtain prior permission from the Government of Haryana and competent authorities.\n1. The cage location must have year-round water availability and a minimum of 8 meters depth.\n1. The applicant should take government permission for rearing exotic fish species. \n\n",
